NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|As to the play, probably, the best way to play the hand is to ruff a diamond and then draw trumps. You can then knock out the K and A of clubs. There is no need to ruff a spade before knocking out the club. The threat is that you might run out of trumps before the clubs were knocked out, and opponents might be able to take a spade or a diamond if you have no more trumps.|
