^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|There is something called the "law of total tricks", which is very useful in deciding whether or not to compete. Simplified, it says that it is safe to bid to the level that equals the number of trumps you have. If you have 8 trumps, it is safe to bid to the 2 level, which is 8 tricks. |
